    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Ultimate Equipment pg. 144</em>, <em>Advanced Player's Guide pg. 288</em></p><p><strong>Aura</strong> faint transmutation <strong>CL</strong> 4th</p><p><strong>Slot</strong> weapon quality; <strong>Price</strong> +1 bonus; <strong>Weight</strong> -</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" title=\"PFS Legal\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\"><strong>Description</strong></h3>When an inquisitor wielder uses her judgment class ability while wielding a <em>jurist </em>weapon, it grants her an enhancement bonus on her Perception checks and to CMD. The bonus is +1 on the first round of her judgment, and increases by +1 each round, to a maximum of +3 on the third and following rounds.</p><p><h3 class=\"framing\"><strong>Construction</strong></h3><strong>Requirements</strong> Craft Magic Arms and Armor, <em>owl's wisdom</em>; <strong>Price</strong> -</p>",
